      <title>大型科技股交易震荡，而选股者却卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/big-tech-trade-shudders-just-as-stock-pickers-make-a-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街 2024 年必胜的赚钱交易——全力押注大型科技公司——本周被颠覆，引发全线股市波动，并在此过程中重创追逐势头的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/big-tech-trade-shudders-just-as-stock-pickers-make-a-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 21:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
